snippet.title: Mortal Shell: Enhanced Edition - Official Reveal Trailer | PS5
snippet.description:
Experience the superior way to play the award-winning Mortal Shell. Uncompromised 60fps gameplay, 4K resolution, and ultra high-quality textures.

Mortal Shell: Enhanced Edition - coming March 4th to PlayStation 5.

Discover more: MortalShell.com

Rated Mature: Blood and Violence, Gore
